# === main-branch-only: develop-side artifacts must not ship ===
# Plugin authoring uses `develop` which carries the paths below;
# `main` is the clean plugin payload for distribution. Even if any
# of these paths appears in the working tree (e.g. after a careless
# checkout from `develop`), .gitignore prevents accidental tracking.
# See ai_context/decisions.md §Branch Strategy on `develop`.
ai_context/
docs/
logs/
.agents/
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
